  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Git分支合并的示意图，展示从底向上的流向。标题就叫\"Simple 'branch and merge' (bottom-to-top)\"吧，这样能清楚表达方向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "gitGraph BT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，BT是bottom-to-top的意思对吧？所以最新的提交会显示在顶部，历史记录在下方。我先建一个main分支，做第一个commit作为起点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit",
        "main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个意思。然后在那个commit的基础上新建一个叫newbranch的分支，切换到上面再做一次提交。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch newbranch",
        "checkout newbranch",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，newbranch已经切出来了，第二个commit也画上去了。现在切回main分支，准备做合并操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后一步，把newbranch合并到main里，这样两条线就汇合了。这个图要的就是展示分支创建和合并的完整流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "merge newbranch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。main分支现在有三个节点：初始commit、合并点，中间newbranch从第一个commit分出去做了独立开发，最后合并回来。方向确实是bottom-to-top，最新的合并提交在最上面。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "merge newbranch",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我再看一眼——合并箭头方向没问题吧？是从newbranch指向main的合并关系，不是反过来？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "merge newbranch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题，merge newbranch这个指令就是把newbranch的内容合并进当前分支main，箭头方向正确。整个流程：main起点 → 开newbranch → newbranch提交 → 回main → 合并，逻辑完整。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "newbranch",
        "merge newbranch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
